  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350 \u001285F (180 \u001285C).",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together flour, salt, and black pepper.",
    "In a large skillet, heat butter over medium heat. Add grated onion, carrot, and zucchini. Cook until tender, about 15 minutes.",
    "Add garlic powder and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Roll out biscuit dough on a lightly floured surface to a thickness of about 1/8 inch. Cut into circles using a cookie cutter or the rim of a glass.",
    "Place dough circles into a 9-inch tart pan with a removable bottom. Trim edges to fit. ",
    "Combine cream cheese, sugar, and unsweetened almond milk in a blender or food processor. Blend until smooth and creamy.",
    "Pour cream cheese mixture into the prepared tart shell. ",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes, or until the edges are golden brown and the filling is set.",
    "Let cool completely before serving."
  ],
